        <title>Cross-View Front Fender-Mounted Mirrors</title>
        <para>The cross-view fender-mounted mirrors (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0901018">Figure 18, Item 1</hotlnk>) are a convex styled mirror located on the front fender
            section of the front end. These mirrors allow a cross-view field of vision for the bus operator during pick
            up and discharge of passengers.
        </para>
